title: Establishment of services enhancing the innovation management capacity of SME's through the Enterprise Europe Network in IRELAND
objective: Our proposal is aimed at providing specialised consulting services for building innovation management capacities in SMEs as well as supporting SME beneficiaries from H2020 funding through the KAM - Key Account Manager - role in overseeing specialist coaching services after assessment on innovation weaknesses.
participants: DONEGAL COUNTY COUNCIL;DUBLIN CHAMBER OF COMMERCE (INCORPORATED);THE CORK CHAMBER OF COMMERCE
